Description:
    Creates a full-features ES6 App out a Boilerplate;
		How it works: Under the hood, it uses Babel and Browserify to transform your ES6 files into ES5 and package them into one file. 
		Creates source maps for ES6 and for LESS.

Options:
    Less: Include Less
    Skeleton: Include Skeleton

Example:
    yo es6-webapp

    This will create:
        gulpfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        app/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.
